descriptionHtml:
Made for DonutAgeOrigins

Feel free to offer feedback, this is just a rough start.

There are a lot of limitations with what I can do with feature shapes (especially nose and mouth) without the CK. 

Pics suck, load it up and try it in-game for best results. Shadows are really bad, especially around the jawline. I made the character in the creation screen, which as you know has a much more washed out and even lighting. Inspecting in-game will allow a better view, and maybe a greater appreciation.

Like I said, it\'s really rough, and most likely will be until the CK.

Mods used in pics

XCE - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2356
CBBE Slim - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666
Beauty Faces (my fav beauty mod) - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1329
Coolsims Retex - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4400

Now Emilia Clarke has some crazy beautiful eyebrows. In my games I use Eyebrows Match Hair - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=627, but if you don\'t have this installed you\'ll get the dark eyebrows from Emilia\'s portrayal in GoT.

Credits go to Bethesda for Skyrim, George R. R. Martin for ASoIaF, HBO for GoT, and Emilia Clarke for being so damned cute.
